{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">One Minute</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Dive into the frantic universe of <u><strong>One Minute</strong></u>, a <strong>roguelite</strong> game like no other where every second counts! Designed to be <strong>fast</strong>, <strong>accessible</strong>, and <strong>addictive</strong>, this game offers an intense experience entirely controlled with your mouse.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83c\udfae <u><strong>Fast and varied mini-games</strong></u>: Face a series of 12 mini-games, each lasting only 5 seconds. Your goal? Achieve the highest score possible!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83d\udcbb <strong><u>Accessibility and performance</u></strong>: Smooth gameplay even on low-end PCs.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83c\udfcb\ufe0f <strong><u>Training mode</u></strong>: Perfect your skills on your favorite mini-games. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83d\udd79\ufe0f <u><strong>Roguelite progression</strong></u>: Earn money by playing and use it to unlock new mini-games or upgrade the ones you already own.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301260/extras/find_shape_evolve_compress_320_x_180.gif?t=1739189572\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83c\udf0d <u><strong>Global leaderboards</strong></u>: Compare your scores with players worldwide, mini-game by mini-game or through an overall leaderboard.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301260/extras/leaderbord_320_x_180.gif?t=1739189572\" /> </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83d\uddb1\ufe0f <u><strong>Unique cursor skins</strong></u>: Earn rare mouse cursor skins after every game, whi